<text top="517" left="170" width="314" height="13" font="0">Malaysia, Maldives, Mauritania, Montenegro, Pakistan, Peru, Poland, Qatar, </text>
<text top="529" left="170" width="314" height="13" font="0">Republic  of  Korea,  Republic  of  Moldova,  Romania,  Sierra  Leone,  Spain, </text>
